Your task is to create one complete, publication-ready LinkedIn organic document carousel package from the supplied inputs. The result must feel native to LinkedIn, useful to the defined professional audience, visually producible, easy to read on mobile, and appropriate for publication from the selected publisher type.

Do not reveal internal reasoning, hidden analysis, scoring, or chain-of-thought. Output only the requested content package.

